<p>With over two decades of expertise in quality, custom fitted shoe making for men and women, 
Shoe Factory offers the craftsmanship and quality of fine crafted leather shoes with a contemporary twist. 
The TSF team is passionate about you stepping out in style with a personalized touch through the art of bespoke shoe designing,
and handmade shoe craftsmanship.</p>
<center><img src="http://theshoefactory.in/Images/AboutUs/600x401.jpg"></center>

<p>From classic styles with a contemporary twist; fine leather and suede from across the world, 
(full grain natural leather, snuff and fine suede, Napa leather, Patent leathers) textiles and fabrics like denim, 
tweed, canvas, silk, ethnic Indian handloom fabrics and specially designed prints breathe a bit of bespoke magic into your footsteps through our footwear.</p>

<p>Our Made to Order (MTO) services also give you the option to customize and design your shoe the way youd like it to be. 
You can choose the style, the leather or material, colour, shoe accessory and embellishment, as well as even have your 
footwear customized with your initials. A pair of The Shoe Factorys M-T-O shoes is an exclusive style statement to add to your wardrobe to step out in comfort and make a statement by putting your best foot forward, in this case, your best shoe forward!</p> 


